Change in-game settings


Parameter | Type | Default | Description
--------- | --------- | --------- | --------- |
premium_confirmation | SettingsPremiumConfirmation |  | Which premium actions should raise a confirmation dialog
language | Language |  | Language
online_status_filter | OnlineStatusFilter |  | Who should see when you're online
extended_simulator | bool |  | Whether combat simulator is toggled to use detailed simulations
music_volume | int |  | Music volume
sound_volume | int |  | Sound volume
ui_sound_volume | int |  | UI sound volume
mute_all | bool |  | Toggle all sound to be muted
time_type | SettingsTimeType |  | Time type to use
time_zone_switcher | int |  | Toggle time zone switcher in the UI
time_format | SettingsTimeFormat |  | Time format to use
attacks_filter | AttacksFilter |  | Filter which attacks you don't want to see on the UI *
map_filter | MapFilter |  | Filter which identifiers on the map you don't wish to see *
enable_tab_notifications | bool |  | Toggle to enable tab notifications on the UI
disable_animations | bool |  | Toggle to reduce animations on the UI
enable_help_notifications | bool |  | Toggle to enable help notifications on the UI
enable_welcome_screen | bool |  | Toggle to enable the welcome screen on the UI
notepads_visible | bool |  | Toggle notepad visibility
_time_zone | float |  | Timezone to use
_time_zone_string | str |  | Timezone string to use

The target and join_condition depend on the attitude of the society

Parameter | Type | Default | Description
--------- | --------- | --------- | --------- |
name | str |  | Name of the secret society
attitude | SocietyAttitude |  | Attitude of the secret society
target | typing.Union[triangulum.utils.enums.BrightSocietyTarget, triangulum.utils.enums.DarkSocietyTarget] |  | Target type of the secret society
target_id | int |  | ID of the target entity
join_condition | typing.Union[triangulum.utils.enums.BrightSocietyAdmissionCondition, triangulum.utils.enums.DarkSocietyAdmissionCondition] |  | Condition type for joining
condition_value | int |  | Value for join_condition
share_battle_and_scout_reports | bool |  | Toggle for whether the society shares battle and scout reports
share_display_of_next_attack_on_village | bool |  | Toggle for whether the society displays the incoming attacks
on eachothers villages
share_additional_village_information | bool |  | Toggle for whether additional information is shared between
the members of the society, such as crop production and troop counts
